<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<%- include('./partials/head.ejs') %>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/index.css">

    <body>
        <div class="headerContainer">
            <header>
                <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>
            </header>
        </div>

        <div class="mainContainer">
            <div class="mainContainerFlavourText">
                <p>Rentals - Israel's leading car rental agency</p>
                <p>Start your journey today</p>
                <a href="/register">Register</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="carPictureContainer"></div>

        <div class="middleParagraphsContainer">
            <div class="paragraphContainer">
                <h2>Special Discounts</h2>
                <p>All registered members of Rentals will receive periodic discounts on booking. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Asperiores voluptatem quae doloremque non vel assumenda.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="paragraphContainer">
                <h2>A Global Enterprize</h2>
                <p>Working with over 900 companies in 160 countries, we can find the right car in the right place, at the right price that suits you best.</p>
            </div>
                <div class="paragraphContainer">
                <h2>Satisfaction Guaranteed</h2>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Eum qui unde fugiat porro perspiciatis autem veritatis aliquid, nemo fuga voluptatibus, eius quibusdam alias repudiandae eveniet quam molestiae excepturi quidem eligendi.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="searchAndResultsContainer">
        <div class="searchFormContainer">
            <form class="searchForm">
                <div class="searchInputsContainer">
                    <div class="labelPlusInputContainer">
                        <label for="">Manufacturer</label>
                        <input type="text" name="" id="manufacturerInput">
                    </div>
                    <div class="labelPlusInputContainer">
                        <label for="">Model</label>
                        <input type="text" name="" id="modelInput">
                    </div>
                    <div class="labelPlusInputContainer">
                        <label for="">Year</label>
                        <input type="text" name="" id="yearInput">
                    </div>
                    <div class="labelPlusInputContainer">
                        <label for="">Transmission</label>
                        <select type="text" name="" id="transmissionInput">
                            <option value="">Select</option>
                            <option value="Manual">Manual</option>
                            <option value="Automatic">Automatic</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="labelPlusInputContainer">
                        <label for="from">From:</label>
                        <input type="date" name="from" id="fromInput" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="labelPlusInputContainer">
                        <label for="to">To:</label>
                        <input type="date" name="to" id="toInput" required>
                    </div>
                    <button class="submitBtn" type="submit">Search</button>
                </div>
            </form>
            <div class="errorContainer"></div>
            <div class="availableInputsContainer">
                <input type="checkbox" name="showUnavailable" id="showUnavailable" class="showUnavailable" onclick="showUnavailable()">
                <label for="showUnavailable">Show Unavailable Cars</label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="resultsContainer"></div>
    </div>
        <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
            <script src="logic/index.js"></script>
    </body>

</html>